      "instruction": "<p>Remove the pan from the heat and stir in<strong> </strong>most of the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (save some for garnish!) – this is your <strong>cacio e pepe sauce</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>drained spinach & ricotta ravioli </strong>to the pan and give everything a gentle mix up until the pasta is coated in the sauce</p>",
